    "en": {
      "title": "A 10-hour ferry to Colombo",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The National Water Supply and Drainage Board has announced that a 10-hour water cut will be implemented tomorrow in some areas under the jurisdiction of the Colombo Municipal Council.",
        "The council informed that this water supply ban will be carried out for essential improvement works.",
        "Accordingly, it has been mentioned that there will be a 10-hour water cut in Colombo 5 and 6 from 11:00 pm on Saturday to 9:00 am on Sunday (21), while water will be distributed with low pressure to Colombo 4. (R)"
      ],
